headline: MarketAxess Reports Record Total Trading Volumes for the Fourth Quarter
summary: MarketAxess closed 2024 with a 6% rise in total credit ADV, driven by strong gains in emerging markets and Eurobonds, despite challenges in U.S. high-yield trading.
